---
// Componente da seção hero
---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="hero-text" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-delay="100">
        <h1>Automatize seus <span class="text-primary">agendamentos</span> e transforme sua produtividade</h1>
        <p>Com a Fluxo, você otimiza todo o processo de agendamentos, reduz falhas e economiza tempo para focar no que realmente importa.</p>
        <div class="hero-buttons">
          <a href="#planos" class="btn btn-primary">Conheça nossos planos</a>
          <a href="#sobre" class="btn btn-outline">Saiba mais</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="hero-image" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
        <img src="/api/placeholder/600/500" alt="Fluxo agendamento automatizado" />
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div class="stat-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
        <h3>98%</h3>
        <p>Redução de falhas de agendamento</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="stat-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="500">
        <h3>75%</h3>
        <p>Tempo economizado em gerenciamento</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="stat-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="600">
        <h3>5000+</h3>
        <p>Usuários satisfeitos</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="hero-wave">
    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 1440 320">
      <path fill="#f9f5ff" fill-opacity="1" d="M0,192L48,176C96,160,192,128,288,122.7C384,117,480,139,576,165.3C672,192,768,224,864,224C960,224,1056,192,1152,165.3C1248,139,1344,117,1392,106.7L1440,96L1440,320L1392,320C1344,320,1248,320,1152,320C1056,320,960,320,864,320C768,320,672,320,576,320C480,320,384,320,288,320C192,320,96,320,48,320L0,320Z"></path>
    </svg>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    padding: 10rem 0 5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5edff 0%, #e6d6ff 100%);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  
  .hero-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 3rem;
  }
  
  .hero-text h1 {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .hero-text p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--text-gray);
    max-width: 90%;
  }
  
  .hero-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  
  .hero-image {
    position: relative;
    animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  
  .hero-image img {
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }
  
  .hero-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 4rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
  }
  
  .stat-item {
    text-align: center;
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
    transition: var(--transition);
  }
  
  .stat-item:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }
  
  .stat-item h3 {
    color: var(--primary-color);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .hero-wave {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    overflow: hidden;
    line-height: 0;
  }
  
  @keyframes float {
    0% {
      transform: translatey(0px);
    }
    50% {
      transform: translatey(-15px);
    }
    100% {
      transform: translatey(0px);
    }
  }
  
  /* Responsividade */
  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .hero-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .hero-text {
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .hero-text p {
      max-width: 100%;
    }
    
    .hero-buttons {
      justify-content: center;
    }
    
    .hero-image {
      margin: 0 auto;
      max-width: 80%;
    }
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero {
      padding: 8rem 0 4rem;
    }
    
    .hero-stats {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-top: 3rem;
    }
  }
</style>
